<h2 id="数组遍历的方法" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#数组遍历的方法"><span>数组遍历的方法</span></a></h2>
<p>在JavaScript中，数组遍历方法有很多，它们各自有不同的用途和特点。以下是一些常用的数组遍历方法，包括它们的基本用法和示例：</p>
<ol>
<li>​<strong>forEach()</strong></li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li>
<p>对数组的每个元素执行一次提供的函数。</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>不会改变原数组，但可以通过回调函数修改原数组（因为操作的是原数组的元素）。</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>没有返回值（undefined）。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="language- line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34"><pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code" v-pre=""><code class="language-"><span class="line"><span>const arr = [1, 2, 3];</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>arr.forEach(item => {</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>  console.log(item * 2); // 2, 4, 6</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>});</span></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><ol start="2">
<li>​<strong>map()</strong></li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li>
<p>创建一个新数组，其结果是该数组中的每个元素调用一次提供的函数后的返回值。</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>不会改变原数组。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="language- line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34"><pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code" v-pre=""><code class="language-"><span class="line"><span>const arr = [1, 2, 3];</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>const doubled = arr.map(item => item * 2);</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>console.log(doubled); // [2, 4, 6]</span></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><ol start="3">
